{"tid":1083996,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國足協新規定　入籍球員須學國歌、明國情、讀黨史、培養愛國情懷","createTime":"2019-03-30T05:12:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-03T01:34:03.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"bdfbfbf93c9a938bf66236d66729d151e8e26707","tid":1083996,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T05:12:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/FOOTBALL-PLAYER-CHINA_dckNM_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FFOOTBALL-PLAYER-CHINA_dckNM_1200x0.jpg&h=b2222f9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n綜合內地新浪及新華社等報道，中國足球協會官方下發《中國足球協會入籍球員管理暫行規定》，要求入籍球員一賽季球員只能以一種身份進行足球比賽，且賽季中不能轉會更改球員身份；入籍球員必須接受中國傳統文化教育並了解國情，學國歌、識國徽與認國旗等。<br />\n<br />\n《規定》要求球會對入籍球員進行中華傳統文化教育，了解中國歷史和國情，制定中文學習計劃，培養愛國主義情懷，入籍球員應能識國旗、認國徽、唱國歌。又要求「俱樂部（球會）所在基層黨組織，應對入籍球員進行黨史、基本理論的普及和教育。俱樂部應指定專人負責入籍球員的思想、生活、訓練、比賽的狀態跟蹤，每月向中國足球協會提交書面報告」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/china/中國足協新規定-入籍球員必學國歌-認國旗-明國情-讀黨史\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%B6%B3%E5%8D%94%E6%96%B0%E8%A6%8F%E5%AE%9A-%E5%85%A5%E7%B1%8D%E7%90%83%E5%93%A1%E5%BF%85%E5%AD%B8%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%8C-%E8%AA%8D%E5%9C%8B%E6%97%97-%E6%98%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%83%85-%E8%AE%80%E9%BB%A8%E5%8F%B2&d=tn6C2tKLXSv13zRFu6un7XjBGfL1Jh2LWroBhk3D7pk%3D&h=43e47d9f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%B6%B3%E5%8D%94%E6%96%B0%E8%A6%8F%E5%AE%9A-%E5%85%A5%E7%B1%8D%E7%90%83%E5%93%A1%E5%BF%85%E5%AD%B8%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%8C-%E8%AA%8D%E5%9C%8B%E6%97%97-%E6%98%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%83%85-%E8%AE%80%E9%BB%A8%E5%8F%B2&h=d760edd0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/china/中國足協新規定-入籍球員必學國歌-認國旗-明國情-讀黨史</a>"},{"pid":"098171e13a3fac5c70b063579c9a4d7544956ade","tid":1083996,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T05:43:31.000Z","ms